flowchart TD
  A[GPT proposes bounded goal] --> B[create_goal]
  B --> C[Goal status: pending]
  C --> D{User approves goal_id?}
  D -- No --> E[reject_goal]
  E --> F[Goal status: rejected]
  D -- Yes --> G[approve_goal]
  G --> H[Goal status: active]
  H --> I[applyProjectEdit]
  H --> J[runProjectCheck]
  H --> K[create_and_approve]
  H --> L[create_raw_and_approve]
  K --> M[command_requests audit]
  L --> M
  I --> N[runProjectGit commit]
  J --> N
  N --> O[writeProjectReport]
  O --> P[close_goal]
  P --> Q[Goal status: closed]
  C -. denied .-> R[auto approval denied]
  F -. denied .-> R
  Q -. denied .-> R
